column2: Supplementary Table 2. Differential gene expression analyses in Dux WT and MZ-KO 2-cell embryos
column18: RPKM: Reads Per Kilobase of gene, per Million mapped reads

Three RNA-seq replicates from each group were used for analyses. Negative binomial test from DESeq R package was used to compute FDR using raw read counts of each gene.  Differentially expressed genes were defined as (RPKM > 1 in either WT or MZ-KO, FDR < 0.05, and FC > 2)
